cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.NE 

This paper is about natural language processing (NLP) and specifically focuses on learning polysemous word embeddings. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also proposes a simple method for learning these embeddings, which could fall under machine learning (cs.LG) or artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper evaluates the proposed method using various tests, which could fall under information retrieval (cs.IR) or neural networks (cs.NE).
